ActCanada Wildlife Act
SubjectEastern Habitat Joint Venture Implementation Agreement
PrecisOrder Providing for the Minister of the Environment to ENTER, on behalf of the Government of Canada, INTO AN AGREEMENT with the governments of the provinces of Ontario, Quebec, Nova Scotia, New Brunswick, Prince Edward Island and Newfoundland and Labrador for the purpose of carrying out activities in support of the implementation of the North American Waterfowl Management Plan, and the North American Bird Conservation Initiative in Canada, pursuant to section 5 of the CANADA WILDLIFE ACT.
